# Git Rule

Antes de commit:

1. Diff review
2. Secrets check
3. `pnpm lint`
4. `pnpm format`
5. `cd apps/devSam && pnpm lint:types`
6. Tests (cuando estén configurados — ver `docs/ai/testing.md`)
7. `pnpm build`
8. Conventional commit

Nunca commitear `.env`, secrets, logs temporales o cambios no relacionados.
